      "description": "<p>Joop Adema, Lasha Chargaziia, Yvonne Giesing, Panu Poutvaara</p>\n<p>ifo institute, LMU Munich, University of Innsbruck<br>_____________________________________________________</p>\n<p>R Version: 4.3.3.<br>For package version control \"groundhog\" package is used. The snapshot date is 2025-04-11.</p>\n<p>_____________________________________________________</p>\n<p>The replication package consists of 4 folders:</p>\n<p>1. 'Data'contains raw (/Raw) and clean (/Clean) datasets used in the study.<br>2. 'Functions' contains custom functions used for the analysis.<br>3. 'Output' contains folders to store generated tables and figures.<br>4. 'Scripts' contains all the scripts used to generate clean data from the raw data, and tables and figures from the clean data.</p>\n<p>_____________________________________________________</p>\n<p>HOW TO USE:</p>\n<p>1. Initiate the project environment with /Destination_choice.Rproj.<br>2. Execute Scripts/Master.R to generate tables and figures used in the paper.</p>",
      "doi": "10.5281/zenodo.15322600",
      "language": "eng",
      "license": {
        "id": "cc-by-4.0"
      },
      "notes": "<p>Data source of address data of Survey II:</p>\n<p>Ausl&auml;nderzentralregister (AZR) provided by the Research Data Center of the Federal Office for Migration and Refugees (BAMF) 2023: Sample from the AZR inventory as of August 31, 2023.<br><br>Data documentation:<br><br>BAMF-Forschungsdatenzentrum (2021): Forschungsvorhaben mit personenbezogenen Daten aus dem Ausl&auml;nderzentralregister: Beantragung und Durchf&uuml;hrung. Arbeitshilfen des BAMF-FDZ Nr. 02/2021. N&uuml;rnberg: BAMF.<br><br></p>",
